# <type>(<scope>): <subject> (max 80 chars)

# <body> (optional)

# <footer> (optional)

# Type: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, perf
# Scope: component or area affected (e.g., nlp, tests, docs)
# Subject: imperative mood, present tense: "add" not "added"
# Body: explain what and why vs. how
# Footer: reference issues, breaking changes
#
# Examples:
#   feat(nlp): add semantic similarity scoring for tag extraction
#   fix(tests): update expectations for improved NLP behavior
#   docs: add comprehensive testing guide
#   chore: update dependencies and clean up cache files